{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"58e3a97f-c512-4ca3-ba5b-a41ca37cdad1","content":"The template is **not quite ready** for NuGet publishing. Issues:\n\n1. **Missing `$schema`** — Add `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"` for tooling validation.\n2. **Missing `groupIdentity`** — Recommended for NuGet so multiple versions/languages can coexist under one identity.\n3. **Missing `precedence`** — Useful when multiple template versions are installed side-by-side.\n4. **Missing `preferNameDirectory`** — Should typically be `true` for project templates.\n5. **No `description`** — NuGet listing will look bare without a short description.\n\nThe core structure (identity, shortName, sourceName, tags, symbols) is valid and functional. It would *work*, but for a polished NuGet package you should add the fields above. Would you like me to update it?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"4bcda66d-dd25-4571-85f2-70aa6b3a8bf2","outputTokens":203,"requestId":"7822:1521D2:B64784:D4376D:69F3FC0B"},"id":"cb01f8b7-812f-4afd-a068-ca63b53eb76f","timestamp":"2026-05-01T01:04:18.856Z","parentId":"9d9db0b4-44aa-4592-b9ad-afb54fc78840"}
